                Counter Improvised Explosive Devices (C-IED), An Enduring Threat</p>
            <p>
                By LTC Bruce W. Nelson, Capability Development Directorate, 
Maneuver Support Protection Division
</p>
            <div class="blockCallout" id="alignRt">
                <div class="blocktitle" id="cap320">
                    </div>
                <div class="blockimage">
                    <asp:HyperLink ID="HyperLink1" runat="server" NavigateUrl="~/app_Inc-Popup/photo-fullsize.aspx?photo=20150622-01-01-0075-01"
